07-24bb-4381-b597-aa33ed09e682" data-is-intersecting="false"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-(--sticky-padding-top)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="e17ab307-24bb-4381-b597-aa33ed09e682" data-turn-id-container="e17ab307-24bb-4381-b597-aa33ed09e682" data-testid="conversation-turn-19" data-turn="user"></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="af5a3431-aa0c-4499-aa93-086d6a3191cd" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="af5a3431-aa0c-4499-aa93-086d6a3191cd" data-turn-id-container="af5a3431-aa0c-4499-aa93-086d6a3191cd" data-testid="conversation-turn-20" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">Thought for 1m 19s<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e6dfed4f-fbba-4efd-9e1a-cc45fbfa3496" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="46">That error makes sense given your constraints:</p>
<ul data-start="48" data-end="337">
<li data-section-id="jjzvyv" data-start="48" data-end="149">
<p data-start="50" data-end="149">You have a <strong data-start="61" data-end="118">unique constraint on <code data-start="84" data-end="116">(course_id, stroke_index, tee)</code></strong> (<code data-start="120" data-end="147">pars_course_si_tee_unique</code>).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sbudr0" data-start="150" data-end="337">
<p data-start="152" data-end="337">The <strong data-start="156" data-end="167">Kinloch</strong> scorecard in your PDF shows <strong data-start="196" data-end="220">stroke index 6 twice</strong> (hole 11 and hole 16), so inserting both rows violates that unique constraint. <span class="relative inline-flex items-center select-none" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_r_ef_" data-state="closed"><button type="button" class="ms-1 relative flex h-[25px] select-none items-center justify-center gap-1 rounded-xl px-2 text-[10px] leading-[13px] corner-superellipse/1.1 text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">NZ Golf Tour - Scorecards (unch…</p></button></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="vbw0f0" data-start="339" data-end="360">What we should do</h3>
<p data-start="361" data-end="566">For Kinloch, one of those “6” values must actually be <strong data-start="415" data-end="420">8</strong> (because <strong data-start="430" data-end="446">8 is missing</strong> from the 1–18 set on the card). To make the data valid under your DB constraints, we need to pick which hole gets SI=8.</p>
<p data-start="568" data-end="707"><strong data-start="568" data-end="611">I’m going to set Kinloch hole 11 SI = 8</strong> and keep hole 16 SI = 6. (This produces a valid 1–18 set and satisfies your unique constraint.)</p>
<p data-start="709" data-end="772">If you’d rather flip it (hole 16 = 8), say so and I’ll swap it.</p>
<hr data-start="774" data-end="777">
<h2 data-section-id="1pdwz2h" data-start="779" data-end="813">SQL Fix + Load (safe to re-run)</h2>
<p data-start="815" data-end="836">This does two things:</p>
<ol data-start="837" data-end="996">
<li data-section-id="1q58kix" data-start="837" data-end="932">
<p data-start="840" data-end="932"><strong data-start="840" data-end="851">Deletes</strong> existing pars for Kinloch <code data-start="878" data-end="887">tee='M'</code> (so we don’t fight the SI unique constraint)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7s2uar" data-start="933" data-end="996">
<p data-start="936" data-end="996">Inserts <strong data-start="944" data-end="965">corrected Kinloch</strong> rows with a full unique SI set</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="998" data-end="2420"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>SQL</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">begin</span><span>;

</span><span class="ͼt">-- Clear Kinloch (tee M) so SI uniqueness won't block insert</span><span>
</span><span class="ͼv">delete</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> pars
</span><span class="ͼv">where</span><span> course_id </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>
  </span><span class="ͼv">and</span><span> tee </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>;

</span><span class="ͼt">-- Re-insert Kinloch with corrected SI set (hole 11 SI changed from 6 -&gt; 8)</span><span>
</span><span class="ͼv">insert</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">into</span><span> pars (course_id, hole_number, par, stroke_index, tee)
</span><span class="ͼv">values</span><span>
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">1</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">13</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">11</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">9</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">6</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">15</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">7</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">17</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">8</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">7</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">9</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">1</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">14</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">11</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">8</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼt">-- was 6 on card; set to 8 to satisfy uniqueness</span><span>
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">12</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">18</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">13</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">16</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">14</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">15</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">16</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>,  </span><span class="ͼy">6</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">17</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">3</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>),
(</span><span class="ͼz">'a845284a-fae0-41a0-a6f8-3ce5cac1be8a'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">18</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼy">12</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼz">'M'</span><span>);

</span><span class="ͼv">commit</span><span>;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
