        </span><span class="ͼ13">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"mx-auto max-w-md px-4 py-6"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><span>
          </span><span class="ͼ13">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"rounded-2xl border p-4 text-sm"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><span>
            Missing or invalid tour id in route.
            </span><span class="ͼ13">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"mt-2"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><span>
              </span><span class="ͼ13">&lt;Link</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"underline"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">href</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/m"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><span>
                Go to mobile home
