<p data-start="783" data-end="837">I do not want to guess which destination you intended.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="z429ta" data-start="839" data-end="875">What I need before providing code</h2>
<p data-start="877" data-end="988">Please provide the full current file that contains the <strong data-start="932" data-end="952">Create Tour form</strong> and inserts into the <code data-start="974" data-end="981">tours</code> table.</p>
<p data-start="990" data-end="1016">It is likely one of these:</p>
