<p data-start="833" data-end="844">This means:</p>
<ul data-start="846" data-end="1043">
<li data-section-id="vf14gh" data-start="846" data-end="908">
<p data-start="848" data-end="908">Creating a tour will open its existing tour management page.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18pture" data-start="909" data-end="964">
<p data-start="911" data-end="964">The Configure button will open the same working page.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8r07uw" data-start="965" data-end="1000">
<p data-start="967" data-end="1000">No database changes are required.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pvv1gb" data-start="1001" data-end="1043">
<p data-start="1003" data-end="1043">Only this one file needs to be replaced.</p>
</li>
</ul>
