<h2 data-section-id="1935xb2" data-start="1896" data-end="1920">Expected final result</h2>
<p data-start="1922" data-end="1998">For HDT5, the mobile landing page would show the image near the top, likely:</p>
<ul data-start="2000" data-end="2078">
<li data-section-id="luqh09" data-start="2000" data-end="2033">
<p data-start="2002" data-end="2033">below the tour name/header; and</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="52b0ie" data-start="2034" data-end="2078">
<p data-start="2036" data-end="2078">above the landing-page navigation buttons.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2080" data-end="2115">Other tours would remain unchanged.</p>
