</span><span class="ͼv">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">HDT5_HERO</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"/tours/hdt5-logo.png"</span><span>;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h2 data-section-id="18m0qh0" data-start="714" data-end="723">Step 3</h2>
<p data-start="725" data-end="768">Inside the existing <code data-start="745" data-end="756">heroImage</code> useMemo add</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="770" data-end="826"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>TypeScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼ11">tourId</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">===</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">HDT5_TOUR_ID</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼv">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">HDT5_HERO</span><span>;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="828" data-end="853">before the default image.</p>
<p data-start="855" data-end="893">That's literally all that is required.</p>
<hr data-start="895" data-end="898">
<h2 data-section-id="19taekt" data-start="900" data-end="917">One suggestion</h2>
<p data-start="919" data-end="987">Your uploaded image is almost square and is mostly white background.</p>
<p data-start="989" data-end="1018">The current landing page uses</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1020" data-end="1112"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>TypeScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span>
    </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼ11">heroImage</span><span>}
    </span><span class="ͼ12">alt</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">""</span><span>
    </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"h-full w-full object-cover"</span><span>
</span><span class="ͼ13">/&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1114" data-end="1158"><code data-start="1114" data-end="1128">object-cover</code> will crop parts of the image.</p>
<p data-start="1160" data-end="1221">For a logo like HDT5 I'd recommend displaying it differently:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1223" data-end="1326"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>TypeScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fec7759e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span>
    </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼ11">heroImage</span><span>}
    </span><span class="ͼ12">alt</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">""</span><span>
    </span><span class="ͼ12">className</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"h-full w-full object-contain bg-white"</span><span>
</span><span class="ͼ13">/&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1328" data-end="1438">or, even better, make <strong data-start="1350" data-end="1372">only the HDT5 tour</strong> use <code data-start="1377" data-end="1393">object-contain</code> while every other tour keeps <code data-start="1423" data-end="1437">object-cover</code>.</p>
<p data-start="1440" data-end="1449">That way:</p>
<ul data-start="1451" data-end="1648">
<li data-section-id="17ebirm" data-start="1451" data-end="1492">
<p data-start="1453" data-end="1492">Scotland poster still fills the screen.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qhvhq2" data-start="1493" data-end="1531">
<p data-start="1495" data-end="1531">Japan poster still fills the screen.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wdevqf" data-start="1532" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1534" data-end="1566">Portugal still fills the screen.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1aaa9lh" data-start="1567" data-end="1595">
<p data-start="1569" data-end="1595">NZ still fills the screen.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fl90nx" data-start="1596" data-end="1648">
<p data-start="1598" data-end="1648"><strong data-start="1598" data-end="1648">HDT5 logo displays perfectly without cropping.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
